    "updated_at": "2016-03-06T18:44:41Z",
    "body": "Thanks @zcbenz, it seems like the one issue with that approach is that it changes the \"base directory\" for resources like `<img src=\"\">`, so that now the browsers loads them relative to the new `path/to/custom/index.html`. I will keep poking around, though.\n"
