    "body": "You can override that behavior using the [base tag](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/base).\n\n``` html\n<base href=\"file://whatever/\">\n```\n\nor\n\n``` html\n<base href=\"http://whatever.com/\">\n```\n\nEdit: Be sure to put this tag in the head before your resources being loaded.\n"
